Get the local admin password for 1 computer from Active Directory PowerShell:
1Get-AdmPwdPassword -ComputerName &lt;computername&gt; Get the local admin password for all computers from Active Directory PowerShell:
1Get-ADComputer -Filter * -SearchBase “OU=,DC=,DC=,DC=” | Get-AdmPwdPassword -ComputerName {$_.Name}
